### Create RxDB Collection with Schema (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs-src/docs/rx-schema.md

This JavaScript snippet demonstrates how to add a collection named 'heroes' to an RxDB database instance using a predefined schema ('myHeroSchema'). It then logs the name of the newly created collection.

```javascript
await myDatabase.addCollections({
    heroes: {
        schema: myHeroSchema
    }
});
console.dir(myDatabase.heroes.name);
```

